title: 06/01/21 DPS Hour 2
itunes:title: 06/01/21 DPS Hour 2
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan shares empathy for young tennis phenom Naomi Osaka, who has recently discussed her struggles with social anxiety and depression. Dan also provides some historical perspective on other professional athletes and their struggles with mental health.
